metadata.name: Blue Roof
metadata.description:
I have been asked several times if I was high while creating this image. I can assure you I do not need any external influence to dream.

My work is characterized by dreamlike otherworldly natural landscapes. My images are fantasy-like but with a hint of realism that evokes a poetic, tantalizing, and intriguing response.
